Package daehee

Class Smile

java.lang.Object
daehee.Smile
public class Smile
extends java.lang.Object
The class contains all Smiley information and the resource to display with Renderer class. This can be further developed into a class where more Smileys can be added. Each instance of Smile represents one particular Smiley.
